<article style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;margin:0px;background-color:white;line-height: 1.5rem;">
  <img style="width: 100%;" src=<%= logoUri %> />
  <h1 style="text-align: center;font-size: 34px; font-style: normal;">Payment Request from <%= companyName %> </h1>
  <div style="padding:0 20px 20px 50px;">
    <p>Dear <%= recipientName %>,</p>
    <p>You have been requested to make a payment of <%= paymentAmount %> for the below reason by <%= companyName %>.</p>
    <p><%= paymentReason %></p>
    <p><a href=<%= url %>>Click here</a> to make this payment. You will be redirected to our payment provider Reapit Ltd. Reapit Payments are powered by Opayo (Sage Pay) for your convenience and security.</p>
    <p>This payment request is valid until <%= paymentExpiry %>. On completion of the payment, our records will be updated accordingly.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p><%= companyName %></p>
  </div>
</article>
